\c 21
\s AbakoBhenjamini bazithathela abafazi
\p
\v 1 Amadoda akoIsrayeli ayefungile-ke eMizipa\x + 20.18. 20.1.\x* esithi: Kakukho lamunye wethu ozanika indodakazi yakhe kuBhenjamini ibe ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 2 Abantu basebesiza eBhetheli, bahlala lapho phambi kukaNkulunkulu kwaze kwahlwa, baphakamisa ilizwi labo bakhala inyembezi ngokukhala okukhulu.
\v 3 Basebesithi: Kungani, O N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kwenzeke lokhu koIsrayeli ukuthi kusilele lamuhla isizwe esisodwa koIsrayeli\x + 20.31.\x*?
\v 4 Kwasekusithi kusisa abantu bavuka ngovivi, bakha ilathi lapho, banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula\x + 20.26. 2 Sam. 24.25.\x*.
\v 5 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesithi: Ngubani ezizweni zonke zakoIsrayeli ongenyukelanga ebandleni eN\nd kosi\nd*ni? Ngoba kwenziwa isifungo esikhulu ngalowo ongenyukelanga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni eMizipa kuthiwa: Uzabulawa lokubulawa\x + 5.23.\x*.
\v 6 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebezisola ngenxa kaBhenjamini umfowabo, bathi: Kuqunyiwe lamuhla isizwe esisodwa sisuke koIsrayeli.
\v 7 Sizabenzelani abaseleyo ngabafazi, ngoba thina sifungile ngeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi kasiyikubanika emadodakazini ethu abe ngomka\add bo\add*?
\p
\v 8 Basebesithi: Yisiphi ezizweni zakoIsrayeli esingenyukelanga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni eMizipa? Khangela-ke kakuzanga loyedwa enkambeni ovela eJabeshi-Gileyadi ukuya ebandleni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1. 31.11-13. 2 Sam. 2.4,5. 21.12. 1 Lan. 10.11.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba abantu babebaliwe, khangela-ke, kwakungekho muntu kubahlali beJabeshi-Gileyadi lapho.
\v 10 Ngakho inhlangano yathuma khona amadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili awamaqhawe amakhulu, bawalaya bathi: Hambani liyetshaya abahlali beJabeshi-Gileyadi ngobukhali benkemba, labesifazana labantwanyana\x + 21.5. 1 Sam. 11.7.\x*.
\v 11 Yile into elizayenza: Lizatshabalalisa wonke owesilisa laye wonke owesifazana owazi ukulala lowesilisa\x + Nani 31.17. Dute. 7.2.\x*.
\v 12 Basebethola phakathi kwabahlali beJabeshi-Gileyadi amankazana angamakhulu amane izintombi ezimsulwa ezingayazanga indoda ngokulala lowesilisa; basebewaletha enkambeni eShilo, eselizweni leKhanani\x + 21.2. Josh. 18.1.\x*.
\v 13 Inhlangano yonke yasithumela yakhuluma labantwana bakoBhenjamini ababesedwaleni leRimoni; bamemezela ukuthula kibo\x + 20.47.\x*.
\v 14 UBhenjamini wasebuya ngalesosikhathi, babanika abesifazana ababebagcine bephila kwabesifazana beJabeshi-Gileyadi, kodwa ngokunjalo kababanelanga\x + Nani 11.22.\x*.
\v 15 Abantu basebezisola ngenxa kaBhenjamini ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayenze ukwehlukana ezizweni zakoIsrayeli\x + 21.6.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Abadala benhlangano basebesithi: Sizabenzelani abaseleyo ngabafazi, ngoba abesifazana bachithiwe koBhenjamini\x + 21.7.\x*?
\v 17 Basebesithi: \add Kumele\add* kube lelifa labaphunyukileyo bakoBhenjamini, ukuze isizwe singatshabalaliswa koIsrayeli.
\v 18 Kodwa thina kasilakho ukubanika abafazi emadodakazini ethu, ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli bafungile besithi: Kaqalekiswe lowo onika uBhenjamini umfazi\x + 21.1. 11.35.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Basebesithi: Khangelani, kulomkhosi weN\nd kosi\nd* eShilo iminyaka ngeminyaka engenyakatho kweBhetheli\x + 20.31.\x*, lapho okuphuma khona ilanga komgwaqo omkhulu\x + 20.31.\x* owenyuka usuka eBhetheli\x + 20.31.\x* kusiya eShekema\x + Josh. 17.7.\x*, langeningizimu kweLebona.
\v 20 Ngakho balaya abantwana bakoBhenjamini besithi: Hambani liyecathama ezivinini,
\v 21 libone, njalo khangelani, nxa amadodakazi eShilo esephuma ukugida imigido, khona lizaphuma ezivinini lizibambele ngulowo lalowo umfazi wakhe emadodakazini eShilo, liye elizweni lakoBhenjamini\x + 11.34. Eks. 15.20. 1 Sam. 18.6. 21.11. 29.5. Jer. 31.13.\x*.
\v 22 Kuzakuthi nxa oyise loba abanewabo befika besola kithi, sizakuthi kibo: Senzeleni umusa ngenxa yabo, ngoba kasibathathelanga ngulowo lalowo umfazi wakhe empini, ngoba lina kalibanikanga wona ngalesisikhathi ukuthi licaleke.
\v 23 Ngakho abantwana bakoBhenjamini benza njalo, bathumba abafazi ngokwenani labo kwabagidayo ababahlwithayo; bahamba babuyela elifeni labo, bakha imizi, bahlala kiyo\x + 20.48.\x*.
\v 24 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebechitheka besuka lapho ngalesosikhathi, ngulowo lalowo waya esizweni sakhe lakusendo lwakhe; basebephuma besuka lapho, ngulowo lalowo waya elifeni lakhe.
\p
\v 25 Ngalezonsuku kwakungelankosi koIsrayeli. Wonke umuntu wayesenza okwakulungile emehlweni akhe\x + 17.6.\x*.